overview:
Julien owns a BA in literature and in communication studies. Throughout his career, he has used his writing skills and communication knowledge to develop a strong expertise in Paid Search and Search Engine Optimization. Prior to Cossette, he worked as an in-house SEO specialist for a leading villa rental wholesaler and as a paid search account manager for a Montreal SEM company. Julienâ€™s years of experience in Search Engine Marketing has allowed him to plan and optimize Search Engine Marketing campaigns on the behalf of more than 30 clients.

He is now the director of Search Marketing at Magnet Montreal. Many Cossette clients including BMO Financial Group, Bell Canada, General Motors of Canada, Canada Post, and Brother Canada have already benefited from his expertise.

Very involve in the industry, he serves as a speaker for many SEM conferences, including Search Engine Strategies (Paris and Toronto) and Infopresse (Montreal). He is also active in the web community where he regularly publishes articles in blogs and reputable news sources.
